==English==
===Etymology===
From ''[[acclimate]]'' + ''[[-ize]]''.

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|acclimatiz|e|}}
# {{intransitive}} To get [[used]] to a new [[climate]].
# {{transitive}} To make used to a new [[climate]] or one that is different from that which is [[natural]]; to [[inure]] or [[habituate]] to other [[circumstance]]s; to [[adapt]] to the [[peculiarities]] of a foreign or strange [[climate]].

